text_cols:
Name: (Last Name, First Name Middle Initial.)
(eg. Dela Cruz, Juan G.)
How would you describe your emotional state during the past two weeks?
What situations or experiences make you feel most hopeless or disinterested?
What kinds of things make you feel anxious or worried, and how do you handle them?
How has anxiety affected your daily activities or interactions with others?
Can you describe times when you felt unusually energetic or driven to take on new activities?
How do these changes in energy or activity level affect your relationships or responsibilities?
Have you noticed any recurring physical discomfort (such as headaches or body pain)? What do you think causes them?
How do your physical sensations or health concerns influence your emotions or thoughts?
How has your sleep pattern changed recently, and what do you think affects it?
What do you notice about your energy or motivation during the day?
num_cols: I easily get irritated or frustrated with others.
I have little interest or pleasure in doing things I used to enjoy.
I avoid situations that make me feel anxious.
I frequently feel nervous, anxious, or on edge.
I start more projects or take more risks than usual.
I sleep less but still have a lot of energy.
I experience unexplained aches or pains such as headaches, back pain, or stomach pain.
I feel my medical problems or symptoms are not taken seriously enough by others.
I have trouble sleeping, or my sleep does not feel restful.
I often feel too tired to complete my usual tasks.
